t.exceptions import NotFoundException` which should be `from kubernetes.client.rest import ApiException` or similar. This affects only test setup, not production code.\n\n2. **Examples Directory**: The examples/hello-agent and examples/math-agent directories exist but are empty. Consider adding example agent code.\n\n### Full Report\n\nA detailed verification report has been written to: `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/VERIFICATION_REPORT_AR026.md`","time":{"start":1775901506965,"end":1775901506965}}}
